\"><p><strong><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Best-Practices-Checklist-eBook.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 105, 162);\">101 Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising Best Practices: A Checklist for Nonprofits</a></strong><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/2025-Best-Practices-Checklist-eBook.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 105, 162);\"> </a>provides 200+ tasks based on the <em>101 Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising Best Practices for Nonprofits</em>\u00a0blog and webinar series.</p></div></div></td></tr><tr  class=\"wptb-row \" style=\"\"><td class=\"wptb-cell \" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding: 10px; width: 107px; border-radius: 0px; \" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"0\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-width=\"false\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-height=\"true\" data-wptb-cell-vertical-alignment=\"center\" ><div class=\"wptb-image-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-image-2\" data-wptb-image-alignment=\"center\" data-wptb-image-size-relative=\"container\"  style=\"\"><div class=\"wptb-image-wrapper\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Tribute-Giving-Report-2025.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"\"  class=\"wptb-link-target\" style=\"float: none; width: 100%; \"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"wptb-image-element-target\" height=\"129\" width=\"100\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Tribute-Giving-Guide-Small.png?resize=100%2C129&#038;ssl=1\"  style=\"width: 100%\" /></a></div></div></td><td class=\"wptb-cell \" colspan=\"1\" rowspan=\"1\" style=\"padding: 10px; border-radius: 0px; \" data-y-index=\"1\" data-x-index=\"1\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-width=\"true\" data-wptb-css-td-auto-height=\"true\" data-wptb-cell-vertical-alignment=\"top\" ><div class=\"wptb-text-container wptb-ph-element wptb-element-text-598\" style=\"color: #3d4645; font-size: 16px; \"><div style=\"position: relative;\"><p><strong>\ufeff<a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/08/Tribute-Giving-Report-2025.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 105, 162);\">How to Launch &amp; Grow a Tribute Giving Program</a>\ufeff</strong>\u00a0provides step-by-step instructions for launching <em>or re-launching</em> a tribute giving program for your nonprofit to better serve your donors and to maximize fundraising success.\u00a0</p></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n\n<hr />\n",
